Creating Lists

var numbers = new List<int>();
var numbers2 = new List<int> { 1, 2, 3, 4 ;

Useful Methods

- Add()         -> Adds an object to the list
- AddRange()    -> Adds a list of objects (can be another list or an array)
- Remove()      -> Removes an object from the list 
- RemoveAt()    -> Removes an object at the given index
- IndexOf()     -> Returns the index of the given object
- Contains()    -> Returns whether the given object exists in the list or not
- Count         -> Returns the number of objects in the list